verses.verse: And this is the <S%H1293>blessing<s%>, wherewith <S%H4872>Moses<s%> the <S%H376>man<s%> of <S%H430>God<s%> <S%H1288>blessed<s%> the <S%H1121>children<s%> of <S%H3478>Israel<s%> <S%H6440>before<s%> his <S%H4194>death<s%>.

And he <S%H559>said<s%>, <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> <S%H935>came<s%> from <S%H5514>Sinai<s%>, And <S%H2224>rose<s%> from <S%H8165>Seir<s%> unto <S%H3313>them<s%>; He shined forth from <S%H2022>mount<s%> <S%H6290>Paran<s%>, And he <S%H857>came<s%> from the ten <S%H7233>thousands<s%> of holy <S%H6944>ones<s%>: At his right <S%H3225>hand<s%> was a <S%H799>fiery<s%> law for <S%H1881>them<s%>.

Yea <S%H637><s%>, he <S%H2245>loveth<s%> the <S%H5971>people<s%>; All his <S%H6918>saints<s%> are in thy <S%H3027>hand<s%>: And they sat <S%H8497>down<s%> at thy <S%H7272>feet<s%>; Every one shall <S%H5375>receive<s%> of thy <S%H1703>words<s%>.
Moses <S%H4872><s%> <S%H6680>commanded<s%> us a <S%H8451>law<s%>, An <S%H4181>inheritance<s%> for the <S%H6952>assembly<s%> of <S%H3290>Jacob<s%>.

And he was <S%H4428>king<s%> in <S%H3484>Jeshurun<s%>, When the <S%H7218>heads<s%> of the <S%H5971>people<s%> were <S%H622>gathered<s%>, All the <S%H7626>tribes<s%> of <S%H3478>Israel<s%> <S%H3162>together<s%>.
Let <S%H7205>Reuben<s%> <S%H2421>live<s%>, and not <S%H4191>die<s%>; Nor let his <S%H4962>men<s%> be <S%H4557>few<s%>.

And this is the blessing of <S%H3063>Judah<s%>: and he <S%H559>said<s%>, <S%H8085>Hear<s%>, <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>, the <S%H6963>voice<s%> of <S%H3063>Judah<s%>, And <S%H935>bring<s%> him in unto his <S%H5971>people<s%>. With his <S%H3027>hands<s%> he <S%H7227>contended<s%> for <S%H5828>himself<s%>; And thou shalt be a help against his <S%H6862>adversaries<s%>.

And of <S%H3878>Levi<s%> he <S%H559>said<s%>, Thy <S%H8550>Thummim<s%> and thy <S%H224>Urim<s%> are with thy <S%H2623>godly<s%> <S%H376>one<s%>, Whom thou didst <S%H5254>prove<s%> at <S%H4532>Massah<s%>, With whom thou didst <S%H7378>strive<s%> at the <S%H4325>waters<s%> of <S%H4809>Meribah<s%>;

Who <S%H559>said<s%> of his <S%H1>father<s%>, and of his <S%H517>mother<s%>, I have not <S%H7200>seen<s%> <S%H5234>him<s%>; Neither did he acknowledge his <S%H251>brethren<s%>, Nor <S%H3045>knew<s%> he his own <S%H1121>children<s%>: For they have <S%H8104>observed<s%> thy <S%H565>word<s%>, And <S%H5341>keep<s%> thy <S%H1285>covenant<s%>.

They shall <S%H3384>teach<s%> <S%H3290>Jacob<s%> thine <S%H4941>ordinances<s%>, And <S%H3478>Israel<s%> thy <S%H8451>law<s%>: They shall <S%H7760>put<s%> <S%H6988>incense<s%> <S%H639>before<s%> <S%H3632>thee<s%>, And whole burnt-offering upon thine <S%H4196>altar<s%>.

Bless <S%H1288><s%>, <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>, his <S%H2428>substance<s%>, And <S%H7521>accept<s%> the <S%H6467>work<s%> of his <S%H3027>hands<s%>: <S%H4272>Smite<s%> through the <S%H4975>loins<s%> of them that <S%H6965>rise<s%> up against <S%H8130>him<s%>, And of them that hate <S%H6965>him<s%>, that they rise <S%H4480>not<s%> <S%H6965>again<s%>.

Of <S%H1144>Benjamin<s%> he <S%H559>said<s%>, The <S%H3039>beloved<s%> of <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> shall <S%H7931>dwell<s%> in <S%H983>safety<s%> by <S%H2653>him<s%>; He covereth him all the <S%H3117>day<s%> <S%H7931>long<s%>, And he dwelleth between his <S%H3802>shoulders<s%>.

And of <S%H3130>Joseph<s%> he <S%H559>said<s%>, <S%H1288>Blessed<s%> of <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%> be his <S%H776>land<s%>, For the precious <S%H4022>things<s%> of <S%H8064>heaven<s%>, for the <S%H2919>dew<s%>, And for the <S%H8415>deep<s%> that coucheth <S%H7257>beneath<s%>,
And for the <S%H4022>precious<s%> things of the <S%H8393>fruits<s%> of the <S%H8121>sun<s%>, And for the precious <S%H4022>things<s%> of the <S%H1645>growth<s%> of the <S%H3391>moons<s%>,
And for the chief <S%H7218>things<s%> of the <S%H6924>ancient<s%> <S%H2042>mountains<s%>, And for the precious <S%H4022>things<s%> of the <S%H5769>everlasting<s%> <S%H1389>hills<s%>,

And for the precious <S%H4022>things<s%> of the <S%H776>earth<s%> and the <S%H4393>fulness<s%> <S%H7522>thereof<s%>, And the good will of him that <S%H7931>dwelt<s%> in the <S%H5572>bush<s%>. Let the blessing <S%H935>come<s%> upon the <S%H7218>head<s%> of <S%H3130>Joseph<s%>, And upon the crown of the <S%H6936>head<s%> of him that was <S%H5139>separate<s%> from his <S%H251>brethren<s%>.

The <S%H1060>firstling<s%> of his <S%H7794>herd<s%>, <S%H1926>majesty<s%> is <S%H7161>his<s%>; And his horns are the <S%H7161>horns<s%> of the <S%H7214>wild-ox<s%>: With them he shall <S%H5055>push<s%> the <S%H5971>peoples<s%> <S%H3162>all<s%> of <S%H657>them<s%>, even the ends of the <S%H776>earth<s%>: And they are the ten <S%H7233>thousands<s%> of <S%H669>Ephraim<s%>, And they are the <S%H505>thousands<s%> of <S%H4519>Manasseh<s%>.
And of <S%H2074>Zebulun<s%> he <S%H559>said<s%>, <S%H8055>Rejoice<s%>, <S%H2074>Zebulun<s%>, in thy going <S%H3318>out<s%>; <S%H3485>And<s%>, Issachar, in thy <S%H168>tents<s%>.

They shall <S%H7121>call<s%> the <S%H5971>peoples<s%> unto the <S%H2022>mountain<s%>; There shall they <S%H2076>offer<s%> <S%H2077>sacrifices<s%> of <S%H6664>righteousness<s%>: For they shall <S%H3243>suck<s%> the <S%H8228>abundance<s%> of the <S%H3220>seas<s%>, And the <S%H2934>hidden<s%> <S%H8226>treasures<s%> of the <S%H2344>sand<s%>.

And of <S%H1410>Gad<s%> he <S%H559>said<s%>, <S%H1288>Blessed<s%> be he that <S%H7337>enlargeth<s%> <S%H1410>Gad<s%>: He <S%H7931>dwelleth<s%> as a <S%H3833>lioness<s%>, And <S%H2963>teareth<s%> the <S%H2220>arm<s%>, <S%H637>yea<s%>, the crown of the <S%H6936>head<s%>.

And he <S%H7200>provided<s%> the first <S%H7225>part<s%> for <S%H2710>himself<s%>, For there was the lawgiver's <S%H2513>portion<s%> <S%H5603>reserved<s%>; And he <S%H857>came<s%> with the <S%H7218>heads<s%> of the <S%H5971>people<s%>; He <S%H6213>executed<s%> the <S%H6666>righteousness<s%> of <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>, And his <S%H4941>ordinances<s%> with <S%H3478>Israel<s%>.
And of <S%H1835>Dan<s%> he <S%H559>said<s%>, <S%H1835>Dan<s%> is a <S%H738>lion<s%>'s <S%H1482>whelp<s%>, That <S%H2187>leapeth<s%> forth from <S%H1316>Bashan<s%>.

And of <S%H5321>Naphtali<s%> he <S%H559>said<s%>, O <S%H5321>Naphtali<s%>, <S%H7649>satisfied<s%> with <S%H7522>favor<s%>, And <S%H4392>full<s%> with the <S%H1293>blessing<s%> of <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>, <S%H3423>Possess<s%> thou the <S%H3220>west<s%> and the <S%H1864>south<s%>.

And of <S%H836>Asher<s%> he <S%H559>said<s%>, <S%H1288>Blessed<s%> be <S%H836>Asher<s%> with <S%H1121>children<s%>; Let him be <S%H7521>acceptable<s%> unto his <S%H251>brethren<s%>, And let him <S%H2881>dip<s%> his <S%H7272>foot<s%> in <S%H8081>oil<s%>.
Thy <S%H4515>bars<s%> shall be <S%H1270>iron<s%> and <S%H5178>brass<s%>; And as thy <S%H3117>days<s%>, so shall thy strength <S%H1679>be<s%>.

There is none like unto <S%H410>God<s%>, O <S%H3484>Jeshurun<s%>, Who <S%H7392>rideth<s%> upon the <S%H8064>heavens<s%> for thy <S%H5828>help<s%>, And in his <S%H1346>excellency<s%> on the <S%H7834>skies<s%>.

The <S%H6924>eternal<s%> <S%H430>God<s%> is thy <S%H4585>dwelling-place<s%>, And underneath are the <S%H5769>everlasting<s%> <S%H2220>arms<s%>. And he thrust <S%H1644>out<s%> the <S%H341>enemy<s%> from <S%H6440>before<s%> <S%H559>thee<s%>, And said, <S%H8045>Destroy<s%>.

And <S%H3478>Israel<s%> <S%H7931>dwelleth<s%> in <S%H983>safety<s%>, The <S%H5869>fountain<s%> of <S%H3290>Jacob<s%> <S%H910>alone<s%>, In a <S%H776>land<s%> of <S%H1715>grain<s%> and new <S%H8492>wine<s%>; <S%H8064>Yea<s%>, his heavens drop <S%H6201>down<s%> <S%H2919>dew<s%>.

Happy <S%H835><s%> art <S%H3478>thou<s%>, O Israel: Who is like unto <S%H5971>thee<s%>, a people <S%H3467>saved<s%> by <S%H3068>Jehovah<s%>, The <S%H4043>shield<s%> of thy <S%H5828>help<s%>, And the <S%H2719>sword<s%> of thy <S%H1346>excellency<s%>! And thine <S%H341>enemies<s%> shall <S%H3584>submit<s%> themselves unto <S%H1869>thee<s%>; And thou shalt tread upon their high <S%H1116>places<s%>.
